{"tid":1859990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隱形病人赴德一傳八","createTime":"2020-02-03T12:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T16:44:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"884e9908ccc409384269c67eeea6b1b2588509f2","tid":1859990,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200203/4JFHNWBAJRYVJV6RUFAN4S5SZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200203%2F4JFHNWBAJRYVJV6RUFAN4S5SZA%2F&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=c539eeac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200203%2F4JFHNWBAJRYVJV6RUFAN4S5SZA%2F&h=fe356c38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200203/4JFHNWBAJRYVJV6RUFAN4S5SZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n隱形病人赴德一傳八<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隱形病人成為武漢肺炎會否引致本港社區爆發的計時炸彈。一名沒有症狀的上海女子，潛伏期間先在德國傳染兩名在同一公司工作的德國男子，其後再間接傳染多六人，即合共八人直接及間接被該名女子傳染。有專家就這宗案例發表研究論文，指出即使沒有症狀的病人也可以是傳播新型冠狀病毒的源頭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：一半非緊急手術料受影響<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200203/large/1580660535_f60b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200203%2Flarge%2F1580660535_f60b.jpg&h=a5866a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由中國撤走的德國人被帶往法蘭克福大學醫院檢查。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潛伏期播毒難堵截<br />\n<br />\n多人中招的德國公司是汽車零件供應商Webasto，位於德國南部的州分巴伐利亞。該公司至今已有七名員工確診武漢肺炎，另有一名確診員工的女兒也被感染。德國專家在《新英倫醫學雜誌》就這宗案例發表研究，論文指出，一名上海女子上月20及21日到德國，在德期間沒有症狀，身體良好，但乘飛機返回中國時感不適，上月26日確診。<br />\n<br />\n一名33歲、健康良好的德國商人，上月20日及21日與該上海女子會面，二人是生意夥伴。該德國男子上月24日開始喉嚨痛、發冷及肌肉痛。翌日發燒至39.1℃，持續咳嗽，同日黃昏他感到身體轉好，27日上班。<br />\n<br />\n該上海女子在1月27日通知該德國公司其病情，德國公司開始追蹤接觸者。至1月28日，德國公司再多三名員工確診，其中一人只與該上海女子接觸過，另外兩人只與該名33歲德國人接觸過。研究指出，案例顯示沒有症狀的病人也可以是傳播新型冠狀病毒的源頭。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病醫生曾祈殷表示，研究顯示沒有症狀的確診病人潛伏期間已可播毒，部份確診者症狀非常輕微，難以堵截。至今未能找出感染源頭的本港75歲居於青衣長康邨病人可能就是受隱形病人感染。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳沛冰"},{"pid":"44d85015e20b3bea23c67ed0079133773d48acf8","tid":1859990,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"上海女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08be16a5cb02ea3284663f5d70adb127f1ab6cdf","tid":1859990,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46222074aecf055963236187a3b48305fa8a4e6","tid":1859990,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"支那又贏"},{"pid":"dbefac996f2283b6270f1b635c66fd9db0dbbf84","tid":1859990,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"德國人好咸濕"},{"pid":"813c424c58863bd31d30232ac0a0eff3bc354b19","tid":1859990,"uid":209662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"去德國做雞。。。"},{"pid":"203ae3cd2abdace469f5fde4038526b6eb0087b4","tid":1859990,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"係德國變左性病"},{"pid":"e2b31d34ab782f303c9cd9a7115d0284c49df4bd","tid":1859990,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"Who：沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f9d022ec23f6a2a96b42f9d8fdaebde92008dc","tid":1859990,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"德國佬有得診 命都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696891cf2c7cca75da66b0cc0b6fdb652a0c12f3","tid":1859990,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"son of the bitch"},{"pid":"5cc17c9f75dbe0422bc66d